Usage: deleteHaloFromBlock [-help] [<inst_name> | -allMacro  | -allBlackBox  | -allCommitPtn  | -allBlock  | -allIOPad  | -cell <name>]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<inst_name>            # block instance name (string, optional)
-allBlackBox           # for all blackBoxs (bool, optional)
-allBlock              # for all blocks (bool, optional)
-allCommitPtn          # for all partitions (bool, optional)
-allIOPad              # for all IO pad (bool, optional)
-allMacro              # for all Macros (bool, optional)
-cell <name>           # by cell name (string, optional)